title: Enjoy Vegan
typeOfFood: Vegan, Pizza, Western, Mediterranean, Juice bar, Take-out, Catering
description: Vegan tapas restaurant, opened 2014. On the menu are fruit juices, pizza, salads, vegan cakes, breakfast food, crepes, tea and infusions. Kitchen uses mainly fruits and vegetables, different types of grain and flour, and nuts. Comida vegetarian.
